S.FORM: Don Bielke nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Don Bielke i 1954 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 8 ku uwac atu silsil 67, namapili' tu nu Fort Wayne Pistons putiput. bulad demiad, 1932 a mihca, Don Bielke, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
